{"tid":2295223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共樂見市民憎恨警察，黑警咪旨意可改善警民關係","createTime":"2020-11-21T15:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T17:49:19.000Z","uid":24730,"like":380,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe68550f0870ac67760b010bfa7cfcf4c090cc7","tid":2295223,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">黑警有槍桿子，亦係香港人，呢啲係支共最唔信任嘅元素，所以支共自去年六月以來增派解放軍嚟香港潛伏，後來又立国安法、派国安嚟，除咗對付市民，最大原因係睇住港警，防止佢地企喺香港人嗰邊，叛變反共，甚至支持獨立，重演辛亥革命新軍起義嘅歷史。<br />\n<br />\n舊年六月以來黑警全面發顛，進入香港人日常生活及居所中襲擊市民、濫捕濫暴，不斷激發更大民憤，唔係因為佢地上級指揮差，而係因為指揮權已落入支共手中，刻意安排各種荒謬行動，刺激市民與黑警對立，令雙方冇可能connect<br />\n<br />\n呢啲暗黑手段，林鄭及警隊高層班政治幼稚園生恐怕一無所知，班偽進出身嘅前線蠢警更加唔會諗到。支共寧可葬送成個警隊，都要防止任何槍桿子出政權嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\nmon post 狗醒定啲，你地唯一岀路係企番香港人呢邊，否則將來支共利用完要清算你地，唔會有香港人會幫你地</span>"},{"pid":"e1c62a6dc2b21cee0178bc6e388135fa22169d37","tid":2295223,"uid":380132,"like":9,"dislike":111,"score":-102,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22fa1b0e8d2871a49fb2cb74e84b610649a7d5c","tid":2295223,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c62a6dc2b21cee0178bc6e388135fa22169d37","tid":2295223,"uid":380132,"like":9,"dislike":111,"score":-102,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 